 in the writing of the plugins, data transmission errors and faulty hardware/drivers. Obviously, the third one should be solved on the user's side.\r\n\r\nBug is rarely reported. Maybe you will find the pattern that can trigger the error for some OBS filter, some PC. Thus you'll be able to stop anyone's stream anytime remotely via the sound effect. But, you know... good luck to you with it! This will be new no streaming protection!.. ^_^\r\n\r\nI only found workaround that if the user has faulty media source - he can add Noise Suppression>Speex filter to it (even with the 0 dB suppression level) to pass the stream to the FFmpeg AAC encoder without triggering the error. Users of other encoders may not experience this error at all (for example, the Core Audio encoder was recommended on the forum long time ago to solve this kind of errors).","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/obsproject/obs-studio/issues/comments/860152381/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"SuslikV","id":19683044,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE5NjgzMDQ0","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19683044?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/SuslikV","html_url":"https://github.com/SuslikV","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SuslikV/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SuslikV/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SuslikV/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SuslikV/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SuslikV/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SuslikV/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SuslikV/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SuslikV/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SuslikV/receiv